org.openscience.cdk.qsar.model.R
Class CNNClassificationModelPredict

java.lang.Object
  org.openscience.cdk.qsar.model.R.CNNClassificationModelPredict
Deprecated. 

public class CNNClassificationModelPredict
extends java.lang.Object

A class that wraps the return value from the R function, predict.nnet for classification models. This is an internal class used by R to return the result of the call to predict.nnet. As a result it should not be instantiated by the user. The actual modeling class, CNNClassificationModel, provides acess to the various fields of this object.

Author:
Rajarshi Guha
Requires:
r-project
Belongs to CDK module:
